<div class="title">How I Became A Closet Drug Addict</div>
<div class="substance">Tramadol, Codeine, Benzodiazepines & Baclofen</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Ashamed+Idiot&Exact=1">Ashamed Idiot</a></div>


